A '''fire umbrella''' is a [[fire dancing]] tool. It is made from an [[umbrella]] with the rainproof cover removed. [[Kevlar]] wicks are attached to the ends of the umbrella, soaked in a fuel, and then lit on fire. The dancer can manipulate the fire umbrella around her or his body, usually twirling it to give the illusion of a spinning ring of fire.<ref>{{YouTube|WPQ5FDO-Sxs|Example of a fire umbrella dance}}</ref>

