{{About|the acrobat/actor|other people named Rafael or Raphael Cruz|Rafael Cruz (disambiguation){{!}}Rafael Cruz}} {{Spanish name|[[Cruz]]}} {{Infobox person |name=Raphael Cruz |image= |image_size= |caption= |birth_name= |birth_date= September 5, 1986 |birth_place=[[Vallejo, California]], [[United States]] |death_date = January 26, 2018 |death_place = [[Paris]], [[France]] |nationality=[[Americans|American]] |occupation=[[Acrobatics|Acrobat]], [[clown]], [[actor]] }}
'''Raphael Cruz''' (September 5, 1986 - January 26, 2018) was an American acrobat, clown, and actor. Cruz is known for having played the lead role of Buster, a [[Buster Keaton]] inspired character, in the [[film|cinema]] themed [[Cirque du Soleil]] production ''[[Iris (Cirque du Soleil)|Iris]]''.<ref name=LAT>{{cite web|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|url=http://framework.latimes.com/2011/09/14/cirque-du-soleil-performers-before-and-after-photos/#/0|title=Cirque du Soleil performers before and after photos|author=Chan, Bryan|date=September 14, 2011}}</ref><ref name=LAT2>{{cite web|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|title=First Look: Costumes for Cirque du Soleil's 'Iris' are part of the spectacle|date=June 16, 2011|author=Lewis, Raha|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/alltherage/2011/06/first-look-costumes-for-cirque-du-soleils-iris-a-journey-through-the-world-of-cinema-are-part-of-the-spectacle.html}}</ref><ref name=OCR>{{cite web|work=[[Orange County Register]]|url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/cirque-318993-iris-most.html|title=Cirque's 'Iris' is a feast for the senses|date=September 26, 2011|author=Hodgins, Paul}}</ref>
Cruz died in Paris on January 26, 2018 from heart and lung failure.<ref name="death">{{citeweb |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/acrobat-actor-raphael-cruz-recently-at-lookinngglass-dies-in-paris/ |title=Acrobat-actor Raphael Cruz, recently at Lookingglass, dies in Paris |website=Chicago Sun Times |date=January 29, 2018 |accessdate=January 29, 2018}}</ref>
